    <div class="content-wrapper max-w-4xl w-[95%] mx-auto mt-10 mb-12 box-border">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-black text-4xl mb-2">Complete Ruby Masterclass</h1>
            <p class="opacity-80 text-xl text-black">From "Hello World" to DSA Foundations (Detailed Edition)</p>
            <a href="https://try.ruby-lang.org" target="_blank" class="compiler-btn block w-full text-center bg-[#238636] text-black py-4 rounded-lg no-underline font-bold text-xl mt-8 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-xl shadow-green-700/30 hover:bg-[#2ea043]">🚀 Open Online Compiler (Practice as you Read)</a>
